00F1F5  2               ; Print byte in A as two hex digits (high nibble first)
00F1F5  2               
00F1F5  2               LAB_PRHEX
00F1F5  2  48                 PHA
00F1F6  2  4A                 LSR                     ; shift high nibble down
00F1F7  2  4A                 LSR
00F1F8  2  4A                 LSR
00F1F9  2  4A                 LSR
